WEBVTT

00:07:56.208 --> 00:08:01.393
and allow it to expand our thinking
about designing symbiotically with nature.

00:08:01.417 --> 00:08:03.018
And by listening,

00:08:03.042 --> 00:08:04.934
we'll only become wiser

00:08:04.958 --> 00:08:08.184
and ready for those
21st-century challenges

00:08:08.208 --> 00:08:13.018
that we know will endanger
our people and our planet.

00:08:13.042 --> 00:08:14.601
And I've seen it.

00:08:14.625 --> 00:08:15.958
I know that it's possible.